Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ドキドキハラハラ こんなのはじめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまで私の 気持ちをもてあそぶの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,無視無視ムリムリ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,突然始まる 大スペクタクル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あっと言わせる為に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,すべてを 賭けてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,每日 大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,お気楽マイペース男の子！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:29.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,とぼけた顔してもダメだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對大迷惑！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,だけど つい見ちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:38.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のこと 気になって！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今度は何にするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:43.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,やめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:04.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}緊張兮兮 神經兮兮 從來沒試過這種感受的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.35,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}你要玩弄人家的感情到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:09.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}無視無視 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.67,0:00:11.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}突然開始的大奇觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}動員自己的一切腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}就是為了讓我大喊一聲「啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:19.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每天都搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:24.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}你這個不安分又特立獨行的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:29.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一臉無辜的表情也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.49,0:00:32.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}絕對在搞怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不過又忍不住看過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:42.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}好在意 你這次又搞什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:43.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不要啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N邊形的內角和是180度 x (N-2)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}而這180度……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小車是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:00:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遙控汽車？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:01:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又把小孩子玩具帶到學校來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課期間玩遙控汽車有沒有常識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這得好好說他才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}多邊形呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君在認真上課
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把玩具丟在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事頭一回啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在學什...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交通規則
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道玩遙控汽車還要先從學習交通規則開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽車駕校？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:02:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,530)\shad0\bord0\c&H1F2123&}第12節課 遙控汽車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君是想考駕照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 在課桌上怎麼可能拿到駕照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能玩得簡單點麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也太講究了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼老半天都不開車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.80,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}開車前一定要檢查車輛安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.52,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}安全行駛第一！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.65,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}S形彎道時要注意內輪差以免撞上路肩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身子都側了 身子都側了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.53,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}L字彎道需要巧妙操作方向盤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.13,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}開上路肩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:14.13,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}先倒車然後再前進的話可以減分了事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去一點也不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得更自由點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就覺得累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.73,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}斜坡起步時需要注意對應斜度的加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他相當消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再試一次就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:58.50,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}駕照考試一天只能參加一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4\bord5\shad0\c&H000000&\pos(132,172)\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\an7}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後用上下面的公式...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在玩遙控汽車了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關君居然同一個遊戲玩兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指上都是創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量特訓的痕跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這已經不是玩耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 還是在玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 開完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在寫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 駕駛證！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連那種東西都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太用心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這麼開心的關君頭一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是假證
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過自己的駕照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那種玩具也有點可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那找同學到前面來做一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那第1問就關來做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那第2第3問誰來呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是自作自受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 要我教麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 我可不會每次都縱容你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的駕駛證
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他答案就給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點小事的話也跟往常一樣習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是允許我參加考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呀 還有個人還沒寫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上課小動作

